<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
</head>
<body>
    <h3>Payment has been made for '<%= @work_order.task_title %>'</h3>
    <p>
        At this stage, your work order has been completed. We hope that everything went smoothly and
        expect that <b><%= @work_order.task_owner_name %></b> is very happy with your work.
    </p>
    <p>
        When you're ready, hop back on <%= site_name %> and <a href="<%= notifications_url %>/#/tasks/search">Search for your next Project</a>
    </p>
    <p>
        Your feedback is always welcome.
        <a href="mailto:<%= @feedback_mailto %>">Drop us a line</a> any time!
    </p>
    <p>
    Sincerely,
  </p>
  <p>
    <em><%= site_signature %></em>
  </p>
</body>
</html>
